President Cyril Ramaphosa addresses the nation Editor's note: The livestream has ended. You can continue watching the recording above PRETORIA - President Cyril Ramaphosa is addressing the nation. The President’s address follows meetings in recent days of the National Coronavirus Command Council (NCCC), the President’s Coordinating Council (PCC) and Cabinet. The President is expected to discuss lockdown measures after the spike in COVID-19 cases and deaths.